snippet.title: Cubesc: Dream of Mira Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer of new Cubesc Puzzle Game. 

Cubesc: Dream of Mira.

A completely new story from the Cubesc universe. You don’t need to have previously played first Cubecs game to enjoy Cubesc: Dream of Mira.

Enjoy beautiful levels, minimal puzzles, using brand new interactions to explore the new Cubesc universe. New dynamics between characters and new cubes.

Cubesc: Dream of Mira is coming out in January 2019.
